		<title>11LEISURE-ADULTS</title>
		<content>   Adults on average spend 11\ hrs     
 pursuing{leisure activities.}The      
 dominant reason was{relaxation.}Other 
 reasons were they were good at it,it  
 gave them{satisfaction, it kept them  
{healthy}or it improved their          
{knowledge.                            
   Many adults followed a number of    
 leisure activities.They are listed    
 below in order of popularity:         
                                       
 Gardening 75%                         
 DIY 60%                               
 Active Sports 55%                     
 Dancing 10%                           
 While in a more passive vein          
 Reading 58%                           
 Sewing 58%                            
 Watching sport 25%                    
 Bingo 15%                             
                                       
